WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.470
Hey, good morning family. Praise the

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:04.390
Lord. Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:04.400 --> 00:00:06.070
Well, we want to take the time right now

00:00:06.080 --> 00:00:08.110
just to thank all our servicemen and

00:00:08.120 --> 00:00:11.270
women. I know a lot of you don't get

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:13.830
enough appreciation. I feel in my heart

00:00:13.840 --> 00:00:16.230
there's a lot of you that are still

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:17.710
going through

00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:22.550
the trials of war, from your body

00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:24.710
being mangled up to all kinds of things.

00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:27.269
You know, there's men that have

00:00:27.279 --> 00:00:29.269
lost their wives, there's women that

00:00:29.279 --> 00:00:31.109
have lost their husbands, and fathers

00:00:31.119 --> 00:00:32.790
and mothers that have lost their sons

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:35.670
and daughters. And I want to

00:00:35.680 --> 00:00:37.709
just take the time to say thank

00:00:37.719 --> 00:00:40.950
you. Thank you. Thank you for

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:43.389
sacrificing your life to make America

00:00:43.399 --> 00:00:46.549
great. Because of people like you, we're

00:00:46.559 --> 00:00:49.510
free. Because of people like you that

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:51.830
have fought in those trenches, and went

00:00:51.830 --> 00:00:51.840
and

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:54.549
got drafted in

00:00:54.559 --> 00:00:56.950
Vietnam, and all the terrible things of

00:00:56.960 --> 00:00:59.549
war, the things that you have

00:00:59.559 --> 00:01:03.349
seen, we pray peace over you today. We

00:01:03.359 --> 00:01:07.630
pray peace over your mind today. We

00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:10.390
pray peace that passes all

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:13.030
understanding over you. I know there's a

00:01:13.040 --> 00:01:14.630
lot of you; you email me and you tell

00:01:14.640 --> 00:01:17.510
me, "I'm battling with PTSD, and I

00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:19.350
have nightmares every

00:01:19.350 --> 00:01:19.360
night."And

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:23.390
my goodness, I pray peace over

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:27.830
you. We know your sacrifice was great,

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:30.030
and

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:33.429
many people will never

00:01:33.439 --> 00:01:35.990
understand that sacrifice because

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:37.390
they've not walked

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:40.149
it. And so we just want to take the time

00:01:40.159 --> 00:01:43.190
to say thank you. Thank you for our

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:45.270
country. Thank you for fighting

00:01:45.280 --> 00:01:46.950
for us. Because of you, we're not

00:01:46.960 --> 00:01:48.469
speaking another language. We're

00:01:48.479 --> 00:01:51.350
Americans and we just want to

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:53.109
say thank you. God bless you. So, we're

00:01:53.119 --> 00:01:54.710
going to go over some of the things that

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:56.870
we spoke about last time in the last

00:01:56.880 --> 00:01:59.910
video. You know, folks, I believe in God

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:03.190
for big. That is my motto. It's

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:05.590
what I teach my kids. That's

00:02:05.600 --> 00:02:07.830
what I teach. That's what my wife and

00:02:07.830 --> 00:02:07.840
I—we

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:10.070
don't want to think small. You know,

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:12.390
it's like Oral Roberts said, "Make no little

00:02:12.400 --> 00:02:15.350
plans here."It's all over his campus.

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:18.949
"Make no little plans here. Think big.

00:02:18.959 --> 00:02:21.110
Think big."So when you drive around,

00:02:21.120 --> 00:02:22.790
it's like Oral Roberts University. You

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.229
can go there so many times. I go out

00:02:24.239 --> 00:02:25.750
there all the time. Drive by every day

00:02:25.760 --> 00:02:28.390
almost and look at the campus because it

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:31.190
inspires me to think and believe

00:02:31.190 --> 00:02:31.200
big—that

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:32.550
that was somebody's faith, you

00:02:32.560 --> 00:02:33.910
know. And so when I talk about driving

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:35.589
around cars, I really don't have a

00:02:35.599 --> 00:02:39.830
desire to have a fleet load of cars,

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:42.390
but I think that's the best the world

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:43.790
has to

00:02:43.800 --> 00:02:46.470
offer: Cadillacs,

00:02:46.480 --> 00:02:47.670
Range Rovers. That's what the

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:49.589
Hollywood movie stars drive, you know.

00:02:49.599 --> 00:02:51.190
And, you know, we don't have a

00:02:51.200 --> 00:02:53.110
Rolls-Royce dealership or Ferrari. I

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:55.910
drive around in those to inspire

00:02:55.920 --> 00:02:58.390
yourself to think bigger. When you're

00:02:58.400 --> 00:02:59.949
raised in

00:02:59.959 --> 00:03:03.229
poverty, when you're raised

00:03:03.239 --> 00:03:06.350
in what I was raised

00:03:06.360 --> 00:03:09.589
in, you don't have an inward image

00:03:09.599 --> 00:03:13.030
of wealth to think bigger for God to do

00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:15.350
bigger because you're so used to

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:17.910
thinking small. You know, grandma was

00:03:17.920 --> 00:03:19.509
poor, her grandma was poor,

00:03:19.519 --> 00:03:20.790
everybody's been poor, and you'll be

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:23.190
poor, too. No, I'm redeemed from the

00:03:23.200 --> 00:03:26.149
curse. And I believe poverty is a curse,

00:03:26.159 --> 00:03:28.390
regardless. I've never seen anybody

00:03:28.400 --> 00:03:30.309
that's not able to pay their bills,

00:03:30.319 --> 00:03:32.470
struggling and eating Spam and doing

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:33.830
things. Well, people say, "I like

00:03:33.830 --> 00:03:33.840
Spam."Well,

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:36.149
I don't. I don't. I personally

00:03:36.159 --> 00:03:38.390
don't. That's my opinion. So you

00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:41.190
know, you have people that

00:03:41.200 --> 00:03:43.589
are raised on certain

00:03:43.589 --> 00:03:43.599
things—Ramen

00:03:43.599 --> 00:03:45.190
noodles and things that you go, "Well,

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:46.869
that's all we had because that's what we could

00:03:46.869 --> 00:03:46.879
afford."Living

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:49.509
on food stamps,

00:03:49.519 --> 00:03:52.229
living on these things. That's a curse.

00:03:52.239 --> 00:03:55.309
True poverty is a curse. It's not a

00:03:55.319 --> 00:03:57.990
blessing. And people, you live in

00:03:58.000 --> 00:04:00.149
some of these remote areas in Haiti and

00:04:00.159 --> 00:04:02.789
Africa and in Asia or

00:04:02.799 --> 00:04:06.149
whatever, and you're living in a

00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:08.670
tin hut or whatever—that's not a

00:04:08.680 --> 00:04:11.429
blessing. I look at what everybody goes

00:04:11.439 --> 00:04:13.750
to work for Monday through Friday. The

00:04:13.760 --> 00:04:15.190
reason I say it, and I'm so strong about

00:04:15.200 --> 00:04:17.349
it, is because we all go to work every

00:04:17.359 --> 00:04:20.789
day to try to make the dream, to get

00:04:20.799 --> 00:04:22.310
enough money to put your kids through

00:04:22.320 --> 00:04:25.590
college, to pay your bills on time

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:28.270
so they don't repo your car. I've been

00:04:28.280 --> 00:04:31.030
there, and I know that those times were

00:04:31.040 --> 00:04:32.749
sorrowful. That was

00:04:32.759 --> 00:04:35.749
hard. And believing God to get extra,

00:04:35.759 --> 00:04:37.749
selling on eBay and Poshmark and doing

00:04:37.759 --> 00:04:39.230
these things that we've

00:04:39.240 --> 00:04:42.909
done, stepping out by faith and finding

00:04:42.919 --> 00:04:46.310
things. There's even another level of,

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:47.950
I see,

00:04:47.960 --> 00:04:50.230
wealth. And the Bible says,

00:04:50.240 --> 00:04:51.909
"Beloved, I wish above all things that

00:04:51.919 --> 00:04:54.310
you prosper and be in health, even as

00:04:54.320 --> 00:04:57.189
your soul prospers."There's so much in

00:04:57.199 --> 00:04:59.670
the Bible about walking in abundance. In

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:02.310
abundance to the full, till it overflows.

00:05:02.320 --> 00:05:04.710
Not living barely getting by and

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:07.430
broke. And yeah, people got you burned

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:09.510
out because of the prosperity preaching

00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:11.350
and all that stuff, but I

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:13.430
believe a lot of them

00:05:13.440 --> 00:05:16.230
started out good, trying to help out

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:18.469
the body of Christ to break off the yoke

00:05:18.479 --> 00:05:20.950
of bondage, because I'm telling you,

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:23.670
there's a lot of bondage with poverty.

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:24.950
And I'm not saying that there's no

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:26.870
bondage with prosperity, because there

00:05:26.870 --> 00:05:26.880
are

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:27.990
a lot of people that

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:32.670
lose themselves in

00:05:32.670 --> 00:05:32.680
it, and

00:05:32.680 --> 00:05:36.310
it is what it is. But I think there's

00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:39.790
a happy medium that you can have

00:05:39.800 --> 00:05:42.150
blessing as long as the blessing doesn't

00:05:42.160 --> 00:05:43.749
have you. So, that's what I'm talking

00:05:43.759 --> 00:05:46.749
about: getting that inward image of the

00:05:46.759 --> 00:05:49.749
blessing and walking in an abundance so

00:05:49.759 --> 00:05:52.469
you can help those around you. Help

00:05:52.479 --> 00:05:54.550
those around you. I've

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:56.710
seen people—man, I wish, you know,

00:05:56.720 --> 00:05:58.710
you drive by and you see somebody that

00:05:58.720 --> 00:05:59.749
they don't have nothing, you're looking

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:01.270
at them going, "Man, I wish I had a little

00:06:01.280 --> 00:06:04.189
extra to help them

00:06:04.189 --> 00:06:04.199
out."But

00:06:04.199 --> 00:06:07.110
there's so much blockage in the

00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:09.029
mind when it comes to the devil trying

00:06:09.039 --> 00:06:11.870
to tell you you can't have

00:06:11.880 --> 00:06:14.550
nothing. He doesn't wrestle with you

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:16.230
trying to bless you. You know what

00:06:16.240 --> 00:06:18.790
happened with me? Let me tell you. I'll

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:21.029
be real with you right now.

00:06:21.039 --> 00:06:23.909
Satan himself came to my house, and

00:06:23.919 --> 00:06:27.110
I used the visions that I

00:06:27.110 --> 00:06:27.120
have—he

00:06:27.120 --> 00:06:30.070
showed me all the wealth. He said, "If

00:06:30.080 --> 00:06:32.950
you bow your knee to me, if you bow your

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:36.150
knee to me, I will give you all this

00:06:36.150 --> 00:06:36.160
wealth."I

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:39.510
saw jets, I saw houses, I saw

00:06:39.520 --> 00:06:41.590
Ferraris, I saw all this. He said, "If

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:43.749
you serve me and use the gift that you

00:06:43.759 --> 00:06:47.110
have for seeing for the kingdom of

00:06:47.120 --> 00:06:49.510
darkness, I will give you everything

00:06:49.520 --> 00:06:51.909
that your heart's desire."He showed it

00:06:51.919 --> 00:06:55.029
all to me. I saw his palace, and it was

00:06:55.039 --> 00:06:57.510
black onyx, and blood was flowing

00:06:57.520 --> 00:06:59.309
from his

00:06:59.319 --> 00:07:02.230
throne, and it was just

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:03.909
similar to

00:07:03.919 --> 00:07:05.510
what happened, I believe, to what happened to Jesus: "If you

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:08.390
serve me, I'll give you all this. I'll

00:07:08.400 --> 00:07:12.469
give you the kingdoms of the

00:07:12.469 --> 00:07:12.479
earth."To

00:07:12.479 --> 00:07:14.309
make a long story short, because I

00:07:14.319 --> 00:07:17.469
don't like talking about the

00:07:17.479 --> 00:07:20.309
darkness, there's nothing the devil has

00:07:20.319 --> 00:07:25.029
to offer in all that that I wanted. I

00:07:25.039 --> 00:07:27.270
want the anointing. I want the presence

00:07:27.280 --> 00:07:30.070
of the Father. And in Him, there's peace.

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:32.309
There's joy. There's all those things.

00:07:32.319 --> 00:07:36.150
The devil has nothing good to offer.

00:07:36.160 --> 00:07:38.350
I've

00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:41.990
had, what, three visitations like that.

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:45.629
The last one was to challenge the

00:07:45.639 --> 00:07:47.749
Word. And he spoke to me, and I said,

00:07:47.759 --> 00:07:49.430
"Are you coming to offer the kingdoms

00:07:49.430 --> 00:07:49.440
again?"And

00:07:49.440 --> 00:07:51.270
he said, "No. Once you

00:07:51.280 --> 00:07:53.430
reject me once, I never come and offer

00:07:53.440 --> 00:07:54.950
you anything again. I'm coming to

00:07:54.960 --> 00:08:00.589
challenge the

00:08:00.589 --> 00:08:00.599
Word."You

00:08:00.599 --> 00:08:03.029
know, like I said, I

00:08:03.039 --> 00:08:05.670
don't talk about the darkness.

00:08:05.680 --> 00:08:07.909
But I want you to know that even the

00:08:07.919 --> 00:08:11.790
devil tries to entice people with

00:08:11.800 --> 00:08:15.110
wealth. Why? Because it's what

00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:17.029
the world wants. We wake up every day,

00:08:17.039 --> 00:08:19.670
Monday through Friday, like I said. But

00:08:19.680 --> 00:08:22.070
how much can you be a believing believer

00:08:22.080 --> 00:08:24.629
and have it, and show the world that you

00:08:24.639 --> 00:08:27.230
can have Jesus and the

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:29.589
blessing? You can have Jesus and the

00:08:29.599 --> 00:08:31.909
blessing. So, that's not my message for

00:08:31.919 --> 00:08:33.589
today, but I feel like a lot of people

00:08:33.599 --> 00:08:35.070
are hung up on

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:37.750
poverty, and I

00:08:37.760 --> 00:08:40.790
refuse to take that vow. I refuse to

00:08:40.800 --> 00:08:42.230
take it for my kids. I want

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:45.110
generational wealth. I'm believing for

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:47.550
what He showed me about the

00:08:47.560 --> 00:08:49.350
cryptocurrencies. I'm believing for what

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:50.509
He showed me

00:08:50.519 --> 00:08:52.949
about gold and silver, and what He showed

00:08:52.959 --> 00:08:55.430
me about these things. And I'm

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:57.430
standing on what the Lord has showed me.

00:08:57.440 --> 00:09:00.949
I stand on that. Now, everything the

00:09:00.959 --> 00:09:03.910
Lord does, it's like I told Dino.

00:09:03.920 --> 00:09:04.870
We were talking about the

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:05.910
anointing and the increase of the

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:08.710
anointing. It seems to go with

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:10.550
the price of the anointing and the price

00:09:10.560 --> 00:09:12.870
of walking in the glory. It seems to go through—you seem to go

00:09:12.880 --> 00:09:15.470
through the

00:09:15.470 --> 00:09:15.480
winepress

00:09:15.480 --> 00:09:19.389
where you feel the pressure of

00:09:19.399 --> 00:09:23.190
things. The character it takes to

00:09:23.200 --> 00:09:27.190
sustain it costs you something.

00:09:30.640 --> 00:09:32.870
You can't get that in the world. You

00:09:32.880 --> 00:09:34.949
can't walk in that kind of glory

00:09:34.959 --> 00:09:37.670
from the world. The devil

00:09:37.680 --> 00:09:40.710
can't offer that. What that is, is it's

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:42.949
coming straight out of the throne room.

00:09:42.959 --> 00:09:44.710
And it was all bought and paid for by

00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:46.550
the blood of Jesus, folks. But I'm

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:48.710
telling you, there is a price to pay for

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:51.430
the anointing. There is a price to pay

00:09:51.440 --> 00:09:55.829
for walking in the glory.

00:09:55.839 --> 00:09:58.790
It comes through pressure. It comes

00:09:58.800 --> 00:10:02.150
through the refiner's fire. And most

00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:04.710
people don't want to hear that. But

00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:06.710
I've studied and I've looked at

00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:08.590
every single

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:10.870
person that has walked in a great

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:12.790
anointing, and they've all had a

00:10:12.800 --> 00:10:15.269
refiner's fire. They've all had pressure

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:17.509
on them to the point where I thought,

00:10:17.519 --> 00:10:19.030
'Does it look like they could make it

00:10:19.040 --> 00:10:19.870
out of

00:10:19.870 --> 00:10:19.880
it?'where

00:10:19.880 --> 00:10:22.310
your head is pulled

00:10:22.320 --> 00:10:25.190
underneath that water and

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:27.430
you're grasping for air, and all you want

00:10:27.440 --> 00:10:29.910
and all you think about is just to get

00:10:29.920 --> 00:10:31.949
your next

00:10:31.959 --> 00:10:35.670
breath. It comes out of that pressure.

00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:38.389
How bad do you want change? How bad do

00:10:38.399 --> 00:10:40.310
you want the glory? How bad do you want

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:43.110
the anointing on your life? It comes

00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:47.269
through something: the press, an oil

00:10:47.279 --> 00:10:49.509
press. Like whenever you see those

00:10:49.519 --> 00:10:50.870
olive oil presses and they're pressing

00:10:50.880 --> 00:10:53.030
that oil, and the more that oil

00:10:53.040 --> 00:10:55.269
presses down on there and clamps

00:10:55.279 --> 00:10:57.750
down on there, it presses all that good

00:10:57.760 --> 00:10:59.790
oil out of those

00:10:59.800 --> 00:11:02.590
olives. That's the way it is with

00:11:02.600 --> 00:11:06.150
you. Staying on the potter's

00:11:06.150 --> 00:11:06.160
wheel,

00:11:06.160 --> 00:11:09.870
staying on that wheel, dying to

00:11:09.880 --> 00:11:13.110
self. He's the potter, we're the clay.

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:14.710
We have this treasure in

00:11:14.710 --> 00:11:14.720
earthen

00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:16.230
vessels, that the excellency of the power

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:18.509
will be known of him and not of

00:11:18.519 --> 00:11:23.670
us. I'm so desperate, and

00:11:23.680 --> 00:11:26.230
I thought, 'Why do I

00:11:26.240 --> 00:11:27.470
want so

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:29.389
badly the

00:11:29.399 --> 00:11:33.190
anointing? Why do I want to see that? Is

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:34.509
it for

00:11:34.509 --> 00:11:34.519
self-glory?'No.

00:11:34.519 --> 00:11:39.190
My heart, when I see children

00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:41.829
with special needs like my Megan, who is

00:11:41.829 --> 00:11:41.839
overcoming—she's

00:11:41.839 --> 00:11:43.269
getting better

00:11:43.279 --> 00:11:44.509
and better every

00:11:44.519 --> 00:11:48.230
